dielectric 1.000000
bond_style harmonic
angle_style harmonic
dihedral_style multi/harmonic
improper_style none
special_bonds lj 0 0 0
pair_modify mix arithmetic tail yes
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify delay 0 every 1 check yes
neigh_modify one 4000
package gpu 1 neigh yes

